\section{Experimental Evaluation}
\label{sec:experiments}

All experiments were run on an Apple M2 with Python 3.11.
All data is in \texttt{paper\_results\_v4/} and reproducible
via \texttt{python3 run\_paper\_experiments.py}.

\subsection{Full Portability Analysis}
\label{sec:portability}

We analyzed all 57 patterns across 10 architectures (570 pairs).
Of these, \textbf{278 (48.8\%) are safe} and
\textbf{292 (51.2\%) exhibit portability bugs}.

